dc_title_s: Plan detaillé du quartier de Ste. Genevieve; levé géométriquement par feu M. l'abbé de La Grive; fini et publié par Al. Fr. Hugnin.
dc_description_s: Shows individual buildings. Shows part of the 5th arrondissement, around the Latin Quarter. "J. P. Ogaer scripsit." 1 map; 49 x 68 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
